{"tid":1990613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【2030 太古城】警圖阻記者拍攝　保安挺身而出","createTime":"2020-04-26T23:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T04:18:28.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"54e883c514d197a229b0ae4fda668ff4f77776d7","tid":1990613,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T23:00:23.000Z","msg":"【2030 太古城】警圖阻記者拍攝　保安挺身而出<br />\n<br />\n今日有網民在太古城中心發起「和你唱」行動，大批軍裝及防暴警員到場驅散市民，並截查多位義務急救員。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》記者於太古城高山臺屋苑平台拍攝警員截查情況，有警察用強光阻礙拍照，又衝上平台試圖阻止記者拍攝。有兩名屋苑保安挺身阻攔警方，被警方指責是騷擾警方執法。警方又要求保安驅趕記者，警告保安必須檢查所有進入屋苑人士住戶証，否則警察就會入屋苑執法。<br />\n<br />\n另看〈太古城「和你唱」　警闖商場驅散　趙家賢助手疑被警方推倒後昏迷送院〉報道全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/426CityPlaza\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F426CityPlaza&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=5144aa04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/426CityPlaza</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3031904083561858/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3031904083561858%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=4ae3d51c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3031904083561858/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"902c82d5a6d4bd595410ed767c97e1fe29c05962","tid":1990613,"uid":99001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"Mark 低佢個名 過年大大封利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c14303b2a9e43351561ed355e46bb6fe729ad8e","tid":1990613,"uid":188176,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T02:30:00.000Z","msg":"所有進入屋苑人士住戶証，否則警察就會入屋苑執法。<br />\n<br />\n你係太古城夠撚膽衝入去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ed0ee5ea6788156ddd60b48f0737d81349cfec","tid":1990613,"uid":35337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"902c82d5a6d4bd595410ed767c97e1fe29c